<DocsLayout title="Developer Docs">
  <h1>Developer Documentation</h1>

  <p>GoldShore exposes a fully Cloudflare-native API that allows you to programmatically control your infrastructure. All endpoints are secured via Service Tokens or Mutual TLS.</p>

  <h2>Getting Started</h2>
  <p>To verify the health of the API, you can make a simple GET request to the health endpoint.</p>

  <CodeBlock lang="bash">
curl https://api.goldshore.ai/v1/health
  </CodeBlock>

  <h2>Authentication</h2>
  <p>Include your API token in the <code>Authorization</code> header.</p>

  <CodeBlock lang="bash">
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" https://api.goldshore.ai/v1/agents
  </CodeBlock>
</DocsLayout>
